pivot_text(zh): 亚美尼亚军团是根据亚美尼亚民族解放运动的目标建立的,该军团是一个武装单位,与亚美尼亚志愿部队和亚美尼亚民兵一起在第一次世界大战期间作战。 他们与奥斯曼帝国作战。
bt_zh: The Armenian legion, which was established in accordance with the objectives of the Armenian National Liberation Movement, is an armed unit that fought during the First World War with the Armenian voluntary forces and Armenian militias, who fought against the Ottoman Empire.
bt_de: The Armenian Legion was founded under the objectives of the Armenian National Liberation Movement and was an armed unit alongside the Armenian Legal Units and the Armenian Militia during World War I, which fought against the Ottoman Empire.

source: Elizabeth Ann Smart (born November 3, 1987) is an American woman who was abducted from her Salt Lake City, Utah bedroom on June 5, 2002 at the age of 14.
pivot_text(de): Elizabeth Ann Smart ist eine Amerikanerin, die am 5. Juni 2002 aus ihrem Schlafzimmer in Salt Lake City, Utah entführt wurde. Zum Zeitpunkt ihrer Entführung war sie 14 Jahre alt.
pivot_text(zh): Elizabeth Ann Smart(1987年11月3日出生)于2002年6月5日在犹他州的盐湖城卧室被绑架,当时她14岁。
bt_zh: Elizabeth Ann Smart, born on 3 November 1987, was abducted on 5 June 2002 in the bedroom of Salt Lake City, Utah, when she was 14 years old.
bt_de: Elizabeth Ann Smart is an American who was abducted from her bedroom in Salt Lake City, Utah on June 5, 2002. At the time of her abduction, she was 14 years old.

source: Further, the term "The Celsius or Centigrade thermometer" was again used in reference to a particular type of thermometer at least as early as 1850.
